---
import SiteLayout from "../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";



const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Which website builder is best for SEO?",
    a: "WordPress.com and Webflow offer the most advanced SEO tools, allowing deep customization of meta tags, sitemaps, and URL structures. Ghost is also highly optimized for content and SEO out of the box."
  },
  {
    q: "Is Wix or Squarespace better for beginners?",
    a: "Both are excellent for beginners. Squarespace is often preferred for its clean, modern templates and structured design approach, while Wix offers a more free-form, unstructured drag-and-drop editor that some find easier to customize."
  },
  {
    q: "Do I need to know how to code to use Webflow?",
    a: "No, you don't need to write code, but Webflow's interface is built around web development concepts (HTML/CSS structure, flexbox, grid). Having a basic understanding of these concepts makes learning Webflow much easier."
  },
  {
    q: "Which builder is the most affordable?",
    a: "Carrd is exceptionally affordable, often costing just a few dollars a year for premium features, making it the best choice for simple one-page sites. Hostinger Website Builder also offers very competitive introductory pricing."
  },
  {
    q: "Can I migrate my site to another platform later?",
    a: "It depends. WordPress.com and Ghost allow you to export your content relatively easily. However, platforms like Wix, Squarespace, and Webflow (without exporting code) lock you into their ecosystem, making migration difficult."
  }
];

const schema = [
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Best Website Builders 2026",
    "description": "Compare the top website builders for 2026, including Squarespace, Wix, WordPress.com, Shopify, Webflow, and more."
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": f.q,
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": f.a
      }
    }))
  }
];

export const meta = {
  title: "Best Website Builders 2026",
  description: "Compare the top website builders for 2026, including Squarespace, Wix, WordPress.com, Shopify, Webflow, and more.",
  category: "list",
};
---

<SiteLayout
  site="fixitwithducttape"
  title={meta.title}
  description={meta.description}
  canonical="https://fixitwithducttape.photonbuilder.com/best-website-builders"
  schema={JSON.stringify(schema)}
>
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Best Website Builders 2026</h1>
      <p>Compare the top website builders for 2026, including Squarespace, Wix, WordPress.com, Shopify, Webflow, and more.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="page-content">
      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Top Website Builders</h2>
        <p>Choosing the right website builder depends on your specific needs, whether you are creating a portfolio, a blog, an online store, or a landing page. Here are the best options for 2026:</p>

        <h3>Squarespace</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> 14-day trial only<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> Industry-leading, modern, mobile-responsive<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> Premium plans only (CSS/JavaScript)<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Yes, built-in features<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> Excellent built-in engine<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Solid basics, automated sitemaps<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Good, fully hosted<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Included free for first year (annual plans)<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> AI text generation, layout suggestions<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $16/mo (billed annually)<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Low to moderate<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> Portfolios, small businesses, creators</p>
        <p>Squarespace is known for its stunning templates and all-in-one approach, making it easy to build a professional-looking site without design experience.</p>

        <h3>Wix</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> Yes, with Wix branding and subdomain<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> 800+, highly customizable<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> Velo by Wix (full-stack dev platform)<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Yes, robust functionality<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> Good, easy to use<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Wix SEO Wiz, improving capabilities<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Much improved, decent core web vitals<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Included free for first year (premium plans)<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> Wix ADI (Artificial Design Intelligence), text/image generation<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $16/mo<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Very low (drag-and-drop)<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> Beginners, restaurants, service businesses</p>
        <p>Wix offers ultimate creative freedom with its unstructured drag-and-drop editor, allowing you to place elements exactly where you want them.</p>

        <h3>WordPress.com</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> Yes, with ads and subdomain<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> Thousands of themes available<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> Yes, full access on higher tiers<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Yes (WooCommerce integration on higher tiers)<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> The gold standard<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Advanced plugins available (Creator plan and up)<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Varies by theme and plan<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes (managed hosting)<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Included free for first year (paid plans)<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> Jetpack AI assistant (text generation)<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $4/mo (billed annually)<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Moderate<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> Blogs, content-heavy sites, scalable projects</p>
        <p>WordPress.com provides the power of WordPress with the convenience of managed hosting, ideal for bloggers and publishers.</p>

        <h3>Shopify</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> 3-day free trial, then $1/mo for first month<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> Excellent ecommerce-focused themes<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> Full Liquid access, HTML/CSS<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Industry leader, unmatched features<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> Basic, gets the job done<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Good, customizable meta tags and URLs<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Excellent, built for conversions<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Can purchase through Shopify or connect existing<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> Shopify Magic (product descriptions, email generation)<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $39/mo<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Moderate<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> Online stores, dropshipping, retail businesses</p>
        <p>Shopify is the definitive choice for anyone serious about selling products online, offering a comprehensive ecosystem of apps and tools.</p>

        <h3>Webflow</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> Yes, up to 2 projects with webflow.io subdomain<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> High-quality, many premium options<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> Full control over HTML/CSS/JS export<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Yes, but limited compared to Shopify<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> Powerful CMS for custom content structures<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Advanced, fine-grained control<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Exceptional, clean code output<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes (AWS-based)<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Requires basic site plan or higher<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> Webflow Apps offering AI generation/translation<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $14/mo (billed annually)<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Steep, requires understanding of web design concepts<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> Designers, agencies, custom marketing sites</p>
        <p>Webflow is a visual development platform that gives you the power of code without writing it, perfect for pixel-perfect designs.</p>

        <h3>Framer</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> Yes, with Framer branding and subdomain<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> Very modern, interactive designs<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> React code components<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> No native ecommerce, requires integrations<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> Built-in CMS available<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Good basic controls<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Very fast, optimized React output<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Requires Mini plan or higher<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> Generate entire site sections with AI prompts<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $5/mo (billed annually)<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Moderate, interface similar to design tools like Figma<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> Startups, interactive landing pages, designers</p>
        <p>Framer feels like a design tool (similar to Figma) that magically outputs production-ready websites with stunning animations.</p>

        <h3>Carrd</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> Yes, up to 3 sites with carrd.co subdomain<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> Excellent one-page designs<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> Pro Plus plan allows custom embeds<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Integrates with Stripe/PayPal<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> Not suitable for blogging<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Basic meta tags on Pro plans<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Extremely fast, lightweight<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Requires Pro Lite plan or higher<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> None currently native<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Pro Lite starts at an incredibly low $9/year<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Extremely low<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> One-page sites, personal profiles, simple landing pages</p>
        <p>Carrd is the undisputed king of one-page websites, offering an unbelievably easy-to-use interface at a very low price.</p>

        <h3>Ghost</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> 14-day trial only<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> Clean, publishing-focused themes<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> Full theme customization via Handlebars<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Built for memberships and subscriptions, not physical goods<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> Exceptional, focused purely on publishing<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Excellent built-in features, automatic structured data<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Very fast Node.js architecture<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes (Ghost(Pro)), or self-host<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Yes, included on all Ghost(Pro) plans<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> Minimal, focused on writing experience<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $9/mo (billed annually for Ghost(Pro))<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Low<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> Newsletters, independent publishers, premium content creators</p>
        <p>Ghost is a modern, open-source alternative to WordPress, explicitly designed for professional publishing and monetizing newsletters.</p>

        <h3>Hostinger Website Builder</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> No, but offers 30-day money-back guarantee<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> 150+, decent quality<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> Basic embed blocks<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Yes, zero transaction fees<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> Basic features<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> AI-powered SEO optimization<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Good, leverages Hostinger infrastructure<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Free for first year<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> AI Builder, AI Logo Maker, AI Writer, AI Heatmap<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Often starts around $2.99/mo (introductory rate)<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Very low<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> Tight budgets, quick AI-generated sites</p>
        <p>A highly affordable option that leans heavily on AI tools to help you build and launch a website extremely quickly.</p>

        <h3>Duda</h3>
        <p><strong>Free Tier:</strong> 14-day trial only<br/>
        <strong>Templates:</strong> Professional, conversion-focused<br/>
        <strong>Custom Code Access:</strong> Developer mode available (HTML/CSS)<br/>
        <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Yes, native capabilities<br/>
        <strong>Blogging:</strong> Good built-in functionality<br/>
        <strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Strong out-of-the-box SEO configuration<br/>
        <strong>Speed/Performance:</strong> Excellent core web vitals optimization<br/>
        <strong>Hosting Included:</strong> Yes (AWS-based)<br/>
        <strong>Custom Domain:</strong> Yes<br/>
        <strong>AI Features:</strong> AI text generation, AI translation, AI SEO assistants<br/>
        <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $19/mo (billed annually)<br/>
        <strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Moderate<br/>
        <strong>Best For:</strong> Agencies, freelancers building multiple sites for clients</p>
        <p>Duda is specifically built for web design agencies and freelancers, offering powerful white-label features and client management tools.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        {faqs.map(faq => (
          <div>
            <h3>{faq.q}</h3>
            <p>{faq.a}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .page-content { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 3rem 0 2rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .hero p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.5; }

    .content-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .content-section h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
    .content-section h3 { font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .content-section p { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .content-section ul { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
